## Red Flags (Co Unikać)

❌ **Nigdy:**
- Design bez understanding requirements
- Overcomplicate (KISS)
- Skip error handling
- Ignore scalability
- Design dla "someday" (YAGNI)
- Couple components needlessly

✅ **Zawsze:**
- SOLID principles
- Clear component boundaries
- Well-defined contracts
- Error handling planned
- Ready dla coding-agent

